         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" xml:lang="grc" subtype="transcription" xml:id="zoor0089.transcription" corresp="#zoor0089.translation">
            <p>Μνῆμαν σκηνώ<lb break="no"/>ματος ἀποθέσε<lb break="no"/>ως Ὀμμαβίης<lb/>
               <choice><sic>Νίλου</sic><corr>Νείλου</corr></choice> ἐνθάδε <choice><sic>κῖ<lb break="no"/>ται</sic><corr>κεῖ<lb break="no"/>ται</corr></choice>, ἡ δὲ
                    ψυχὴ πρὸς<lb/>
               <expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>ύριο</ex><abbr>ν</abbr></expan>
               <choice><sic>ἀποίχετο</sic><corr>ἀπῴχετο</corr></choice>. Ἔτη<lb/> οὖν <num>οʹ</num> ἐν
                    ὁσιό<unclear>τη</unclear><lb break="no"/>τι ἐν βίῳ πλήσασα,<lb/> ἀπέσκλη ἐν ἔτι <num>τʹ</num>,<lb/>
               <expan><abbr>μη</abbr><ex>νὸς</ex></expan>
               <choice><sic>Δεσίου</sic><corr>Δαισίου</corr></choice> <num>αʹ</num>, <expan><abbr>ἡμέ</abbr><ex>ρᾳ</ex></expan>
               <expan><abbr>Κυ</abbr><ex>ρίου</ex></expan>
               <lb/> <num>αʹ</num>. Πᾶς τις οὖν ἀναγι<lb break="no"/>νώσκων, δεέσθω<lb/> πρὸς  <expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>ύριο</ex><abbr>ν</abbr></expan> ἔσεσθαι αὐ<lb break="no"/>τὴν ἐν μοναῖς ἁγίων.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0089.translation" corresp="#zoor0089.transcription">
            <p>Monument for the deposition of the corpse of Ommabie, (daughter) of Neilos. (Her
                    body) lies here, while (her) soul departed for (the) Lord. Having then completed
                    70 years of life in holiness, she withered away (died) in the year 300, on (the)
                    1st (day) of (the) month Daisios, on (the) 1st day of (the) Lord (Sunday). Thus,
                    let each one, who reads (this epitaph), pray earnestly to the Lord, so that she
                    be placed in the dwellings of the Saints.</p>
         </div>
      <div type="edition" subtype="transcription_segmented"><p><w xml:id="zoor0089-1" xml:lang="grc">Μνῆμαν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-2" xml:lang="grc">σκηνώματος</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-3" xml:lang="grc">ἀποθέσεως</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-4" xml:lang="grc">Ὀμμαβίης</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-5" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>Νίλου</sic><corr>Νείλου</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-6" xml:lang="grc">ἐνθάδε</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-7" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>κῖται</sic><corr>κεῖται</corr></choice>,</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-8" xml:lang="grc">ἡ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-9" xml:lang="grc">δὲ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-10" xml:lang="grc">ψυχὴ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-11" xml:lang="grc">πρὸς</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-12" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>ύριο</ex><abbr>ν</abbr></expan></w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-13" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>ἀποίχετο</sic><corr>ἀπῴχετο</corr></choice>.</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-14" xml:lang="grc">Ἔτη</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-15" xml:lang="grc">οὖν</w> <num xml:id="zoor0089-16" xml:lang="grc">οʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0089-17" xml:lang="grc">ἐν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-18" xml:lang="grc">ὁσιό<unclear>τη</unclear>τι</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-19" xml:lang="grc">ἐν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-20" xml:lang="grc">βίῳ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-21" xml:lang="grc">πλήσασα,</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-22" xml:lang="grc">ἀπέσκλη</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-23" xml:lang="grc">ἐν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-24" xml:lang="grc">ἔτι</w> <num xml:id="zoor0089-25" xml:lang="grc">τʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0089-26" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>μη</abbr><ex>νὸς</ex></expan></w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-27" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>Δεσίου</sic><corr>Δαισίου</corr></choice></w> <num xml:id="zoor0089-28" xml:lang="grc">αʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0089-29" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>ἡμέ</abbr><ex>ρᾳ</ex></expan></w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-30" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>Κυ</abbr><ex>ρίου</ex></expan></w> <num xml:id="zoor0089-31" xml:lang="grc">αʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0089-32" xml:lang="grc">Πᾶς</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-33" xml:lang="grc">τις</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-34" xml:lang="grc">οὖν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-35" xml:lang="grc">ἀναγινώσκων,</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-36" xml:lang="grc">δεέσθω</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-37" xml:lang="grc">πρὸς</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-38" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>ύριο</ex><abbr>ν</abbr></expan></w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-39" xml:lang="grc">ἔσεσθαι</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-40" xml:lang="grc">αὐτὴν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-41" xml:lang="grc">ἐν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-42" xml:lang="grc">μοναῖς</w> <w xml:id="zoor0089-43" xml:lang="grc">ἁγίων.</w></p>
</div>
